<p>Tom St. Amand at <a href="https://nitter.rawbit.ninja/ILMVFX" title="Industrial Light & Magic">@ILMVFX</a> adjusts one of the figures riding a flying BMX for E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial (1982). While the wheels and pedals were animated with go-motion, traditional stop-motion was used for the figures.</p>
